thresher shark
Homonym Number:  1
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:also called mango ripi, a shark noted for the large upper fluke on its tail
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also sea-fox
